snippet.title: World Exclusive Reveal: Abiotic Factor Dark Energy Update – PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
Half-Life-inspired survival sim Abiotic Factor gets a major new update in February next year, one that sheds new light on your lab’s parent organisation GATE. If you can survive their cleanup operation, that is.
